PrecisAppointment of HUBERT SAINT-ONGE, of Richmond Hill, Ontario; SHELDON BOWLES, of Winnipeg, Manitoba; and ROSEMARY PENELHUM, of Bragg Creek, Alberta, not employed in the Public Service, as governors of the Canadian Centre for Management Development, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
